author: Anjana George
title: Two unique numbers in ‘St Peter’s Day’
text:
Sajan K Mathew's debutant movie 'St' Peters Day', a comedy-action thriller that cast Asif Ali and Aju Varghese narrating the lives of two orphan guys will have two songs written by Rafeeque Ahmed .
Talking about the songs, music composer Vinu Thomas says that it is giving him a novel experience. "It has a rock song and a family number which are very important in the story of the cinema. Working on two different genre song is exciting and the same time challenging!" he adds.
